I"A<h1 id="github-pages">Github Pages</h1>

<p>You can use the millidocs theme with github pages by adding it as a <code>remote_theme</code>.</p>

<pre><code>---
title: Millidocs Theme
description: Documentation for small projects
url: "https://my-url"

remote_theme: alexander-heimbuch/millidocs

markdown: kramdown
kramdown:
  syntax_highlighter_opts:
    disable : true

exclude:
  - Gemfile
  - Gemfile.lock
  - README.md

---
</code></pre>

<p>For more details visit the <a href="https://blog.github.com/2017-11-29-use-any-theme-with-github-pages/">Github Blog Post</a>.</p>
